Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,橘你真是不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,根本一點也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我約會一次試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定很噁心的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你會跟我約會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 是啊 約會之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才說「跟我約會一次試試看」對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的…剛才呢是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你說過了對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧我說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正细圆_GBK\an7\fs30\bord0\frz270\c&HD9C6A5&\b1\pos(1020,340)}羅生門\N作者\N芥川龍之介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個家將 在羅生門下避雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,寬廣的門下 除他之外沒有別人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只在朱漆斑駁的大圓柱上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,蹲著一隻蟋蟀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,羅生門橫跨著朱雀大道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,除了他之外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,本該另有幾個戴女笠和軟烏帽的行人來此避雨才對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可是除他之外 再沒有別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正细圆_GBK\an7\fs25\bord0\c&HC3B8BB&\b1\frz287.4\pos(582,219)}店長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正细圆_GBK\an7\fs25\bord0\c&HC3B8BB&\b1\frz287.4\pos(559,237)}晶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 您說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,您說得太對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 今後一定加倍小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好的…那我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,加瀨啊 你就不能把頭髮剪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我下次去剪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你上次也是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 我貼了新的換班表 記得看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,店長 你週六休息對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了新的換班表…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯 我那天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我也休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你說…要和我約會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…那只是舉個例子而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就週六怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,週六?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,週六約會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…這個呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,請你和我約會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,…好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那就請多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 零工?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經有一份了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 家教是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一小時多少錢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 還可以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是輔導高中生?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是英語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,倒不是幹不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 有點意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那高中生挺可愛的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼是男的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,高中生當然得性別女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,現在都沒客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼非得教男的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,上個月的都輸光了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,玩老虎機輸的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 這也太慘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,加瀨你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大塚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,橘 吃點什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,三明治 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,橘晶 高二學生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,年紀輕輕卻格外冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,基本一張撲克臉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,小橘 飯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她在看什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…加瀨 這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,額外贈品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真冷淡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs25\bord0\c&H232323&\pos(255,184)}七月 排班表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs20\bord0\c&H7785C6&\b1\pos(1040,101)}在前廳\N{\c&H9D8BC5&}保持微笑\N{\c&H7785C6&}開心快樂\N精神飽滿!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 就休息好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你在學習?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,高中課本太令人懷念了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看完就放那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 請問幾位?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吸煙還是禁煙?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,禁煙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊 請隨意就座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,上課的時候塗鴉 這可不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,能不告訴別人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…也不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可相對地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你得和我約會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,加瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 今天放學了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,原來你回去換了衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.07,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}I Was a Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,據說還挺嚇人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,受得了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕了的話 儘管摟著我的手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟工作日 人真少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是去美甲沙龍了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,尼桑 快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她已經不是我們認識的安潔莉卡了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,胡說八道!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,安潔莉卡 是我啊 還記得嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,記得的話就快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 安潔莉卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼? 這就回去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子不餓嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,家母準備了晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,電影票 小冊子和可樂的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,至少喝杯茶吧 這可是約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,橘你是田徑部的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,受傷了才退部的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,吉澤說你跑得可快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,都是過去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經痴迷的事物突然在某一天化為泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎樣的感受?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,惹你生氣的話 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都過去了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時很失意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但現在不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,打工也挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因為店長?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我倆今天第一次對視
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經按約定和你約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該會保守秘密吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這也叫約會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是失去了心愛的田徑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,又找到了心愛的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的王子卻是個四十五歲的大叔…不噁心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你也不用付錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,說了等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,來電話了 對方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,…店長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想接?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是花園的近藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,現在方便嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,方便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就是上次那件事…約…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,…約會的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼想去的地方嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去哪我就想…去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那我想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 勞煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你就這麼喜歡他?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是在使壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想說…戀愛 還是健全一點吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,建議而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就放過你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們下次繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這電影看起來有點刺激啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼隨手一丟 不收起來?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去丟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我是花園的近藤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,見面地點應該就是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,…好想抽煙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,去稍微抽一支好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 要是她在這時候來就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,…店長 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看你和平時的感覺不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,…因為我換了個…髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是去美甲沙龍了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,尼桑 快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她已經不是我們認識的安潔莉卡了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,胡說八道!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,安潔莉卡 是我啊 還記得嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,記得的話就快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,…安潔莉卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,尼桑!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你想 帶著勇斗的話 就看不了這種電影了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得看多少遍都會很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們回去吧 電影也看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,…我渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.03,Comment,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,您需要點什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一杯柳丁冰茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,乞…力馬扎羅咖啡 熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,最近老花眼有點嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真抱歉 年紀大了就有股味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,橘你平常都來這裡的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的…偶爾來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,店長 多少個?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.95,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an7}註：日語裡詢問個數和年齡的說法相同（いくつ）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 我四十五啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:30.05,Comment,,0,0,0,,一塊 兩塊 三塊 四塊 五塊 六塊 七塊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…原來說的是糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這個味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次約會的時候 耍帥點了黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但果然還是覺得苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,趁她去廁所的時候 往裡擱了不少糖來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,甜裡透著苦 是青春的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 剛才那電影啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那可真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這家店怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼都是年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,店長?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,收據不用給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,您說?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,容我接一下電話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 橘…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我不禁悲從中來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是她的年輕和單純
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 對不再年輕的自己的不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…我必須回店裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不只因為在意周圍的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,最大的理由 是我不想受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定覺得很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我這種大叔約會 不無聊才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,甜中帶苦的青春已逝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,留下來的只有苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那…我們花園見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,晶 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,又去看了一遍?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說很無聊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一本是今天的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要混在一起!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我不是讓你把之前那本丟了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一本不都一樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡一樣了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定…不一樣啊…
